<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="question-vt">question <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'kwestʃən/    美 /'kwestʃən/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>询问；审问：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He was questioned by the police.
他受到警方的审问。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>怀疑；对...表示疑问：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>No one questioned his ideas for almost 2,000 years.
将近2000年，没有人怀疑过他的看法。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Soon you will also question whether the voice you're hearing is actually real.
不久你也会怀疑你听到的声音是否不是真人。</p><footer>2019 北京</footer></div></div>